OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FShowers clearing to the south
OL,6,Fof Orkney in the morning to leave a
OL,7,Fdry day with sunny spells for all
OL,8,Fareas. Light to moderate easterly
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry with some late sunshine
OL,12,Fat first this evening then clear
OL,13,Fspells after sunset. Dry overnight
OL,14,Fwith clear periods before becoming
OL,15,Fcloudier over Shetland later. Light to
OL,16,Fmoderate easterly winds.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FA dry and settled day with
OL,19,Flight winds. It will be mostly cloudy
OL,20,Fbut some bright and sunny spells
OL,21,Fbreaking through.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
